Doctor Who - Big Finish Podcast 08 - 04-22-2008

Big Finish Podcast - Episode 8
(22/04/2008)
In this weeks Big Finish Podcast we preview Skull of Sobek and The Haunting of Thomas Brewster, Nick Briggs gives us his top 5 while speaking to Barnaby Edwards and later in the show, Barnaby goes through the feedback and we play our first voicemail! If that isn&amp;#039;t enough for you, Paul goes out and about and speaks with Nigel Fairs and John Dorney and we talk about the new series of Sapphire and Steel. All that and the latest in Big Finish news.

